Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Children{\i}   解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾如風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徐如林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵掠如火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動如山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對可憐{\i1}Children{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以給我等著吧  雪山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼因果關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且雪山又不會跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  還是開車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要特意滑雪過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要撒嬌  因為山在那邊等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開車的話  馬上就能到那座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪過去也沒什麼關係啊  我們是人類嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明到了之後想怎麼滑都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據GPS顯示  應該是在這附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會遇到暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用瞬移一下子飛到目的地去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的暴風雪有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才說要開車去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:01:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大好的年輕人不要這麼快就累垮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還拉著兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊  這華麗的三圈半迴轉跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超群的美貌和技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那也不是滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊超能力者  明石薰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解禁中止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制器  ON
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳太過依賴超能力了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.15,0:01:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去  累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼回去啊  都來到這裡了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那個了
